'''Arcil''' neɣ '''Tissulya''' neɣ asali s teqbaylit d asdukel n sin [[afgan|yemdanen]] deg yiwen wexxam. Asali yettili ger wergaz d tmeṭṭut. Tikwal yiwen wergaz d snat neɣ kṛad neɣ ukkuẓ n tlawin. Acku Tineslemt d asɣan n wagut n yiqbayliyen iwumi defka azref i wergaz akken ad-yaɣ ukkuẓ n tlawin maca yessefk ad-yesseẓref gar-asent.

Iqbayliyen sseqdacen awal asali seg wemyag suli meḥsub zweǧ. Amedya : leflani yessuli axxam, meḥsub yezweǧ, yuɣ tamettut.

Win neɣ tin ara yessalin neqqar-as isli, tislit . asget islan, tislatin.
